, THE COMPANY HAD A REFINING NETWORK CAPABLE OF PROCESSING NEARLY 2 MILLION BARRELS OF CRUDE OIL PER DAY. OPERABLE CAPACITY AT DECEMBER 31,

2014

, AND DAILY REFINERY INPUTS FOR

