2014

WAS 87 PERCENT, COMPARED WITH 84 PERCENT IN

2013

. AT THE U.S. REFINERIES, CRUDE OIL DISTILLATION CAPACITY UTILIZATION AVERAGED 91 PERCENT IN

2014

, COMPARED WITH 81 PERCENT IN

